{"tid":1025893,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"小米手機第一！是關於手機輻射測試","createTime":"2019-02-17T16:14:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-18T03:01:48.000Z","uid":221827,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"860837237b1b09e60dc5a6a3ce71e5077830b5ea","tid":1025893,"uid":221827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T16:14:39.000Z","msg":"製作手機由於零件中可能存有放射性物料，手機輻射成為一直存在，但較少人留意的問題。雖然有關手機輻射對用家有害之說未有科學證實，但用家還是可以參考美國手機輻射 1.6 W/kg 標準，對健康更有保障。最近德國聯邦輻射防護辦公室，對 2018 年 12 月 10 日前，推出的多個品牌手機作輻射值測試，結果小米 A1 獲得第一。<br />\n<br />\n從列表上可以看到，小米手機有多款產品成功上榜，分別是第一的小米 A1、小米 MAX 3、小米 MIX 3 及紅米 Note 5，至於在海外市場做得不錯的 OnePlus，OnePlus 5T、OnePlus 6T 及 OnePlus 6 都榜上有名。<br />\n<br />\n至於輻射最低的手機，反而大部份都是 Samsung 手機，中國品牌手機 ZTE，亦有多部手機的輻射水平是偏低，不知這樣會不會影響大家入手手機時的決定呢？<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.dcfever.com/news/readnews.php?id=24375\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dcfever.com%2Fnews%2Freadnews.php%3Fid%3D24375&d=MHEGAcVJLkfiWkVsZ9yRxq0EM2ZTCgB2Df5M2YAuo3Y%3D&h=0ac2059b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.dcfever.com/news/readnews.php?id=24375</a><br />\n<br />\n強國又<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6908d7e39512efb28ae39d52a3e19093b0a0edd7","tid":1025893,"uid":221827,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T16:15:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn01.dcfever.com/articles/news/2019/02/190212_mia1_03.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn01.dcfever.com%2Farticles%2Fnews%2F2019%2F02%2F190212_mia1_03.jpg&h=38811d43&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn01.dcfever.com/articles/news/2019/02/190212_mia1_02.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn01.dcfever.com%2Farticles%2Fnews%2F2019%2F02%2F190212_mia1_02.jpg&h=f42b1ddd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2a50a648931ec700bdb432623534157f00c14623","tid":1025893,"uid":54574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T16:16:48.000Z","ms